.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, rock-climbing
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk
2 different pets are kept: lizard, pony
1. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | collecting |
| Beverage   | 7up     | soy-milk     |
| Pet           | pony          | lizard     |

