.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-20::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, romance
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, techno
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, begonia
1. the person watching action movies is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of techno is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | action | romance |
| Music-Genre   | disco  | techno  |
| Flower     | begonia | balloon-flower    |

 